---
title: Plant-Based Basil Pesto & Pumpkin Fettuccine with Chilli-Garlic Pangrattato & Rocket Salad
description: Who let the kitchen fairy in last night because they’ve worked their magic and summoned a bowl of golden fettuccine pasta. The roasted pumpkin in a creamy sauce and the fresh basil pesto will enchant you, so go on have a bite and fall under its spell.
